How it works

  1. 1. Sign up

    Create your seller account and set up your store — it's simple and open to everyone.

  2. 2. Sell your products

    Host live shows, list products, run promotions, and build your audience.

  3. 3. Ship and get paid

    Use prepaid WhatNew labels and cash out via direct deposit 48–72 hours after delivery.

{/* FAQ */}

Frequently asked questions

How do I get paid?

You’ll get paid 48–72 hours after your package is delivered. Payments appear as WhatNew credit, which you can cash out.

How does shipping work?

We partner with carriers to provide prepaid labels so shipping is painless.

What are the fees?

8% commission on sold price + 2.9% + ₹0.30 processing on the transaction.

Is it safe?

Yes — we provide tools and support to keep transactions secure.
